<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.7.2">
<l>āḷum paramaṉai kaṇṇaṉai yāḻip pirāṉṟaṉṉait</l>
<l>tōḷumōr nāṉkuṭait tūmaṇi vaṇṇaṉem māṉṟaṉṉait</l>
<l>tāḷun taṭakkaiyuṅ kūppip paṇiyu mavarkaṇṭīr</l>
<l>nāḷum piṟappiṭai tōṟemmai yāḷuṭai nātarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The Highest one who rules, Kṛṣṇa, the lord with the discus</l>
<l>the one the colour of a pure sapphire with once four arms, our lord,</l>
<l>those who humble themselves before him, folding the feet and hands, see,</l>
<l>are daily in every birth the leaders who have us as servants.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
